<para>Configuration data union. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This union holds a pointer to the specific configuration data struct required for the selected haptic source. The correct member must be populated before calling <ref refid="group__drv2605__interface_1gafe7decc53e258a7162b44ae2076c10d1" kindref="member">drv2605_haptic_config()</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
